OL,3,CIslanders conquer 24-hour charity
OL,4,Cgaming marathon in Guernsey
OL,6,FA team of video gamers in Guernsey
OL,7,Fhave conquered a 24-hour gaming
OL,8,Fmarathon to raise money for a men's
OL,9,Fmental charity.
OL,11,FMore than 30 islanders took part in
OL,12,Fthe 17th 'Guernsey Gaming for Good'
OL,13,F(GG4G), organised by Digital
OL,14,FGreenhouse with proceeds going to
OL,15,FMen's Shed, which offers men
OL,16,Fopportunities to come together and
OL,17,Fsocialise through a variety of
OL,18,Factivities with the aim of boosting
OL,19,Ftheir sense of purpose and mental
OL,20,Fwellbeing.
