OL,3,CIslanders conquer 24-hour charity
OL,4,Cgaming marathon in Guernsey
OL,6,FThe event started at 10am yesterday
OL,7,Fmorning (19 October).
OL,9,FSince GG4G was set up as an
OL,10,Forganisation in 2014, it has raised
OL,11,Fover #32,000.
OL,13,FLast year over #6,000 was raised for
OL,14,Fthe Royal British Legion and Channel
OL,15,FIslands Airsearch.
OL,17,FThe event's organiser James Hookway,
OL,18,Fcaptured the sense of excitement in
OL,19,Fthe room as the marathon kicked off
OL,20,Fyesterday morning.
