OL,3,CIslanders conquer 24-hour charity
OL,4,Cgaming marathon in Guernsey
OL,6,FJames told ITV News: "The first 12
OL,7,Fhours are always quite electric, I
OL,8,Flike to say. There's always an
OL,9,Fexcellent atmosphere, everyone's
OL,10,Fperky, everyone's good to go. It gets
OL,11,Fto midnight, the sun goes down, every
OL,12,Fstarts to slow down there but the
OL,13,Fbiggest challenge is always the 4am to
OL,14,F5am slot, that's when no-one's smiling
OL,15,Fanymore and it's just faces looking at
OL,16,Fscreens in front of them and it's a
OL,17,Fvery sombre atmosphere!"
