OL,6,FThe whole event was livestreamed so
OL,7,Fpeople around the world could cheer on
OL,8,Ftheir friends taking part in the event
OL,9,Fand donate.
OL,11,FKyle Gallie, one of the seasoned
OL,12,Fgamers, even got dressed up for the
OL,13,Fchallenge.
